    "name": "Summit Hopper",
    "steam_appid": 3104220,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >It's a long way to the summit..</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Summit Hopper </i>is a precision platforming journey where every hop must be executed with precise timing and pinpoint accuracy. Navigate through intricately designed dynamic environments, each with unique modifiers requiring constant strategic adjustment. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Punishing platforming</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The higher you ascend, the harder you fall. Time your jumps carefully as the power in a jump not only changes how high you reach but also the angle you launch at. Although this can be difficult to learn, it can be mastered.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104220/extras/efc52973cc7635ffca1d6b3d0ff3947b.poster.avif?t=1743668749\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104220/extras/efc52973cc7635ffca1d6b3d0ff3947b.webm?t=1743668749\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104220/extras/efc52973cc7635ffca1d6b3d0ff3947b.mp4?t=1743668749\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Adapt your approach</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Different obstacles will require new tactics. Only mastering precise jumping will not bring you to success. Environmental modifiers will also force a change in pace multiple times throughout your journey.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104220/extras/adc4c5b559d05778faca37e163e2ce36.poster.avif?t=1743668749\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104220/extras/adc4c5b559d05778faca37e163e2ce36.webm?t=1743668749\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104220/extras/adc4c5b559d05778faca37e163e2ce36.mp4?t=1743668749\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Physics</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Interactions with realistic physics at some points as a static environment would be too kind.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Ambience</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unique Environments</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Many different environments and interactive effects with distinct atmosphere and audio throughout. A diverse world that you explore as you ascend.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104220/extras/346ce832a2ca8a13f5b3a5dfc235dc5a.poster.avif?t=1743668749\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104220/extras/346ce832a2ca8a13f5b3a5dfc235dc5a.webm?t=1743668749\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104220/extras/346ce832a2ca8a13f5b3a5dfc235dc5a.mp4?t=1743668749\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Calm and Rage</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Peaceful moods with calming tunes just in case you get stuck for awhile. On the other hand, sometimes you are taunted when you fall..</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A Different Ending..</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A special conclusion for those who reach the summit. Many games in this genre feature an underwhelming finale. A substantial effort was made to detach from this status quo.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Addendum</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A special thanks to the authors that allowed the referencing of their game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104220/extras/8184506328252b56798fe9e8b7162a4e.poster.avif?t=1743668749\" width=416 height=110 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104220/extras/8184506328252b56798fe9e8b7162a4e.webm?t=1743668749\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>",
